        <div class="body">
            <p>Not this way...
Once you created an currency you can not change the currency representation just with an locale.</p>

<p>You need to create a new currency with the expected locale or you can override the currency representation per hand with the setFormat parameters.</p>

<p>But toCurrency can not change the representation of the currency, only how the numbers are formatted.</p>

